- feature in systems manager

- This is a secure storage for parameters and secrets

- optional encryption

- control user and resource access using  IAM

- referrable through multiple aws accounts

Parameter Vs Secrets Manger

- Similarities
  - stores values up to 4096 characters
  - values encrypted with kms
  - referrable in cloudformation

- Parameter
  - No additional cost ( free )

- Secrets manager
  - Built in passowrd generator
  - great for cross account access
  - automated secret rotation
